#. [scenario]: id=00_Being_Born
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:5
msgid "Being Born"
msgstr "Zrození"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The Heart Mountains have the word Heart in their name for a reason. This is "
"the largest mountain range in the known world, forming a natural wall that "
"splits the Northlands in two."
msgstr ""
"Srdcové hory nezískaly své jméno jen tak. Jedná se o největší pohoří ve "
"známém světě, které tvoří přírodní zeď rozdělující Severní země na dvě části."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:24
msgid ""
"This vast expanse of craggy hills and mountain peaks is home to many "
"dwarves, who are usually engrossed in a feverish search for ever rarer ores, "
"or else getting themselves drunk on honey."
msgstr ""
"V těchto rozlehlých končinách skalnatých kopců a horských vrcholů žije mnoho "
"trpaslíků, kteří se většinou věnují horečnatému hledání stále vzácnějších "
"rud nebo opíjení medovinou."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Other creatures also live in the shadows of the dark caves and earthy "
"grottos. Creatures great and terrible in appearance, but naive in nature, "
"and easy to manipulate."
msgstr ""
"Ve stínech temných jeskyní a zemitých grott žijí i další bytosti. Bytosti "
"mohutného a děsivého vzezření, avšak povahy naivní a snadno manipulovatelné."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:32
msgid ""
"These are trolls. They are often thought of as beasts, bloodthirsty monsters "
"who only do bad things, but this is not true at all. As I have said before, "
"they are merely naive... and perhaps sometimes a little bit too reckless."
msgstr ""
"To jsou trollové. Často se o nich mluví jako o bestiích, krvežíznivých "
"monstrech, jimž ve stopách kráčí smrt a zkáza. Pravda je však jiná. Jak jsem "
"již řekl, jsou prostě jen naivní... a někdy jednají poněkud bezhlavě."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:37
msgid ""
"The story I am about to tell you happened sixteen years after we, humans, "
"first came to the Great Continent. This is a story of the evil that pursued "
"us here, and the sadness that has come to the trolls..."
msgstr ""
"Příběh, který vám nyní povím, se odehrál šestnáct let poté, co jsme my, "
"lidé, poprvé přišli na Velký kontinent. Je to příběh o zlu, které nás sem "
"pronásledovalo, a o neštěstí, které trolly postihlo..."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:39
msgid "Crelanu the Wise"
msgstr "Krelanu Moudrý"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:51
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:48
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:43
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:68
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/04_A_Beautiful_World.cfg:41
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/04_A_Beautiful_World.cfg:111
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/Secret.cfg:45
msgid "Golden Flame Tribe"
msgstr "Kmen Zlatého plamene"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:63
msgid "Newborn"
msgstr "Novorozený"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:73
msgid "One day in the Heart Mountains."
msgstr "Jednoho dne v Srdcových horách."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:99
msgid "In a silent moment, a stone wall came to life."
msgstr "V tiché chvíli ožila kamenná stěna."

#. [unit]: type=Strong Troll Whelp, id=OL_PROLOG
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:107
msgid "Nameless Troll"
msgstr "Bezejmenný troll"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:124
msgid "...And it suddenly shattered."
msgstr "... a najednou se roztříštila."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:141
msgid ""
"The newborn troll began to crawl. He moved very slowly. It was as if he was "
"still dreaming, or as if his inner flame had only just begun to warm."
msgstr ""
"Novorozený troll se začal plazit ve snaze prozkoumat okolí. Zpočátku jen "
"velmi pomalu. Všechno mu připadalo jako vzdálený sen. Počáteční nejistotu "
"postupně potlačila zvědavost a tělo bytosti začalo pociťovat hřejivý pocit, "
"jenž mu dodával sílu."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:168
msgid ""
"With each step, his flame of life grew stronger. The troll’s heart shimmered "
"with golden light."
msgstr ""
"S každým krokem jeho životní plamen sílil. Srdce trolla začalo zářit zlatým "
"světlem."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:188
msgid "The newborn wanted to roar, but he knew no words."
msgstr "Novorozený chtěl řvát, neznal však slov."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:242
msgid "Turning, the newborn realized he was alone."
msgstr "Když se rozhlédl, uvědomil si, že je sám."

#. [message]: speaker=OL_PROLOG
#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:247
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:839
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:670
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:258
msgid "He tried again to speak and... This time he succeeded."
msgstr "Pokusil se znovu promluvit a... Tentokrát se mu to podařilo."

#. [message]: speaker=OL_PROLOG
#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:267
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:208
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:715
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:527
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:1091
msgid "Ougl!!"
msgstr "Ougl!!"

#. [modify_unit]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:274
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/utils/characters.cfg:6
msgid "Ougl Firstborn"
msgstr "Ougl Prvorozený"

#. [message]: speaker=OL_PROLOG
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:291
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:696
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:767
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:361
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:883
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/04_A_Beautiful_World.cfg:306
msgid "...?"
msgstr "...?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:337
msgid "New motion suddenly disturbed the underground calm."
msgstr "Nový pohyb náhle narušil klid v podzemí."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:360
msgid ""
"As if prompted by Ougl’s roar, other trolls also awoke from their sleep."
msgstr ""
"Jako povoláni Ouglovým řevem se i ostatní trollové začali probouzet ze svého "
"spánku."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/00_Being_Born.cfg:397
msgid "This is how trolls are born."
msgstr "Takto se rodí trollové."

#. [scenario]: id=01_First_Steps
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:5
msgid "First Steps"
msgstr "První kroky"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:27
msgid "As the first awakened, Ougl became the leader of his tribe."
msgstr "Jakožto první probuzený, stal se Ougl vůdcem svého kmene."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:31
msgid ""
"The children of stone moved forward. Their path — not an easy one — led "
"through intricate corridors deep underground. They did not know light, for "
"it never reached these deep places. The air was cold."
msgstr ""
"Kamenné děti se vydaly na cestu. Jejich kroky vedly spletitými chodbami, "
"které se vinuly nekonečnými útrobami podzemní říše. Neznali světlo, neboť do "
"takové hloubky nemohlo proniknout. Vzduch byl chladný a tichý."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:36
msgid ""
"When the Golden Flame Tribe (as I will henceforth call them) entered tunnels "
"that had once belonged to the bearded race, one of the trolls began to "
"behave quite unusually."
msgstr ""
"Když kmen Zlatého plamene (jak jej budu odteď nazývat) vstoupil do tunelů, "
"které kdysi patřily vousaté rase, jeden z trollů se začal chovat poněkud "
"neobvykle."

#. [side]
#. [unit]: type=Fire Guardian, id=IF
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:71
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:390
msgid "Inner Flame"
msgstr "Vnitřní plamen"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:104
msgid "Ash Flame Tribe"
msgstr "Kmen Popelavého plamene"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:132
msgid "Cave Dwellers"
msgstr "Obyvatelé jeskyní"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:163
msgid "Defeat the Inner Flame and Ash Flame leaders"
msgstr "Poraz vůdce Vnitřního a Popelavého plamene"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:167
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:170
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1152
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:295
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:645
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/Secret.cfg:96
msgid "Death of Ougl"
msgstr "Ougl zemře"

#. [unit]: type=Troll Whelp, id=AU
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:226
msgid "Arru"
msgstr "Arru"

#. [unit]: type=Troll Whelp, id=GO
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:243
msgid "Gao"
msgstr "Gao"

#. [unit]: type=Troll Whelp, id=NM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:260
msgid "Nuum"
msgstr "Nuum"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:277
msgid "Suddenly, one of the trolls began to behave strangely."
msgstr "Najednou se jeden z trollů začal chovat podivně."

#. [unit]: type=Troll Whelp, id=UG
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:283
msgid "Strange Troll"
msgstr "Divný troll"

#. [message]: speaker=UG
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:357
msgid "Ullg!!"
msgstr "Ullg!!"

#. [modify_unit]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:384
msgid "Ullg the Flameless"
msgstr "Ullg bez plamene"

#. [message]: speaker=IF
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:440
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:818
msgid "S s s s...!"
msgstr "S s s s...!"

#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:479
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1268
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/Secret.cfg:614
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/utils/defeat.cfg:27
msgid "Ougl?"
msgstr "Ougl?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:635
msgid "H i s s...!"
msgstr "S s s s...!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:702
msgid "The finder of the mysterious egg made a decision without much thought."
msgstr "Nálezce podivného vejce učinil rozhodnutí bez dlouhého přemýšlení."

#. [unit]: type=Fire Ant, id=LA
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:736
msgid "Lonely Ant"
msgstr "Osamělý mravenec"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:773
msgid ""
"There are many unexplainable things in this world. This is one of them: the "
"little ant decided to join the trolls."
msgstr ""
"Na tomto světě je spousta nevysvětlitelných věcí. Tohle je jedna z nich: "
"malý mravenec se rozhodl přidat ke trollům."

#. [message]: speaker=UG
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:830
msgid "Ullg...!"
msgstr "Ullg...!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:845
msgid ""
"Ougl has learned how to control his inner flame. You can now recruit <b>Fire "
"Guardians</b>."
msgstr ""
"Ougl se naučil ovládat svůj vnitřní plamen. Nyní můžeš rekrutovat "
"<b>plamenné strážce</b>."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:856
msgid ""
"Also... some of the trolls, like their leader, began to feel a mysterious "
"connection to fire. You can now recruit <b>Troll Initiates</b>."
msgstr ""
"Navíc... někteří trollové, stejně jako jejich vůdce, začali pociťovat "
"tajemné pouto s ohněm. Nyní můžeš rekrutovat <b>trollí novice</b>."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:874
msgid ""
"There is an open trapdoor in the ruined dwarven castle. Do you want to go "
"through it and play the bonus puzzle level?"
msgstr ""
"V troskách trpasličího hradu jsou otevřené padací dveře. Chceš jimi projít a "
"zahrát si bonusový scénář zaměřený na logické myšlení?"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:876
msgid "I will play the bonus puzzle scenario."
msgstr "Zahraju si bonusový logický scénář."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/01_First_Steps.cfg:887
msgid "I don’t want to play the bonus puzzle scenario."
msgstr "Nechci hrát bonusový logický scénář."

#. [scenario]: id=02_A_Dream
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:5
msgid "A Dream"
msgstr "Sen"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Soon Ougl saw that they had come to a dead end. The way forward was blocked "
"by rock and stone."
msgstr ""
"Ougl brzy zjistil, že se dostali do slepé uličky. Cesta vpřed byla "
"zablokována skalami a kameny."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:26
msgid ""
"There were two options. The trolls could either turn back the way they came "
"or... break through."
msgstr ""
"Měli dvě možnosti. Mohli se buď vrátit zpět, kudy přišli, nebo... prorazit "
"skrz."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:31
msgid "Of course, they chose the latter."
msgstr "Samozřejmě si vybrali druhou možnost."

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:74
msgid "Grove Guardians"
msgstr "Strážci háje"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:99
msgid "Emmm the Oak"
msgstr "Dub Emmm"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:100
msgid "Ummm the Birch"
msgstr "Bříza Ummm"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:101
msgid "Immm the Linden"
msgstr "Lípa Immm"

#. [unit]: type=Wose Shaman, id=OM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:106
msgid "Ommm the Oldest"
msgstr "Nejstarší Ommm"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:166
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1148
msgid "Survive until turns run out"
msgstr "Přežij do konce kol"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:180
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1166
msgid ""
"If a Fire Guardian or Fire Wraith moves on a forest or grass tile it will "
"partially burn down. Enter a tile twice to completely burn it down."
msgstr ""
"Pokud se plamenný strážce nebo ohnivý přízrak přesune na políčko s lesem "
"nebo trávou, dojde k jeho částečnému spálení. Pokud na ně vstoupí dvakrát, "
"spálí pole úplně."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:184
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1170
msgid ""
"The grove area has a special time of day: Mystic Light, which gives lawful "
"units bonus +25%, and chaotic -25%."
msgstr ""
"V oblasti háje panují v určitou denní dobu zvláštní podmínky. Mystické "
"světlo zde poskytuje zákonným jednotkám bonus +25 % a chaotickým jednotkám "
"postih -25 %."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:188
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1174
msgid "Woses teleport from the castle through the Great Trees."
msgstr "Stromovci se přemisťují z hradu skrze velké stromy."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Now that Ougl was able to control his inner flame, he could easily break "
"through stone walls."
msgstr ""
"Nyní, když se Ougl naučil ovládat svůj vnitřní plamen, dokázal bez problémů "
"prorazit kamenné zdi."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:363
msgid "First the stone wall was heated, and then Ougl smashed it."
msgstr "Nejprve se kamenná zeď zahřála a pak ji Ougl rozbil."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:369
msgid "I have no idea why such a thing should work, but it made sense to Ougl."
msgstr ""
"Netuším, jak něco takového mohlo fungovat, ale Ouglovi to smysl dávalo."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:625
msgid ""
"Ougl broke through the rocks again and again until he opened a way to a very "
"mysterious place."
msgstr ""
"Ougl znovu a znovu prorážel skály, dokud si neprorazil cestu na velmi "
"tajemné místo."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:631
msgid ""
"They were no longer as deep underground as before and the darkness was not "
"as thick."
msgstr ""
"Již nebyli tak hluboko pod zemí jako předtím a tma zde nebyla tak hustá."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:721
msgid ""
"Ougl loved this strange new green color, and there was plenty of it here."
msgstr ""
"Ouglovi se nová podivná zelená barva moc líbila a tady jí byla spousta."

#. [unit]: type=Wose, id=AM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:732
msgid "Ammm the Maple"
msgstr "Javor Ammm"

#. [message]: speaker=AM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:757
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1253
msgid "A m m m...?"
msgstr "A m m m...?"

#. [message]: speaker=AM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:786
msgid "A m m m...!"
msgstr "A m m m...!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:792
msgid ""
"Ougl could not guess what the leafy creature might want from him and his "
"brothers, for Ougl could not speak or understand the language of other "
"beings. He only knew feelings and emotions."
msgstr ""
"Ougl nemohl přijít na to, co by ta listnatá bytost mohla chtít od něj a jeho "
"bratrů, neboť Ougl nedokázal mluvit ani rozumět jazyku jiných bytostí. Znal "
"pouze pocity a emoce."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:803
msgid ""
"...And from moment to moment he felt more and more anger from the tree folk, "
"which waved its branches menacingly at the nearby Fire Wraith."
msgstr ""
"S každou vteřinou cítil stále větší hněv ze strany stromového lidu, který "
"výhružně ukazoval větvemi na nedaleký ohnivý přízrak."

#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:817
msgid "Ougl...?"
msgstr "Ougl...?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:833
msgid "There was nothing left for the trolls to do but defend themselves."
msgstr "Trollům nezbývalo nic jiného než se bránit."

#. [unit]: type=Wild Saurian, id=RE
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1076
msgid "Refumee the Swampling"
msgstr "Refumee z močálu"

#. [message]: speaker=RE
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1098
msgid "S y s y...!"
msgstr "S y s y...!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1109
msgid ""
"The Saurian’s speech meant nothing to Ougl, but Ougl felt that he could "
"trust and rely on her. He felt that the swamp dweller was not hostile and "
"wanted to support him."
msgstr ""
"Ačkoli Ougl nerozuměl jazyku ještěřice, podvědomí mu říkalo, že jí může "
"věřit. Cítil, že obyvatelka bažin k němu není nepřátelská a chce mu pomoci."

#. [message]: speaker=RE
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1121
msgid "S y s y..."
msgstr "S y s y..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1137
msgid ""
"The young trolls spotted a huge tree within the underground forest. This was "
"one of the great woses, the guardians of the grove, and it glared menacingly "
"at the stone creatures who it believed were threatening saplings."
msgstr ""
"Mladí trollové zahlédli v podzemním lese obrovský strom. Byl to jeden z "
"prastarých stromovců, strážců háje, a hrozivě se díval na kamenné tvory, o "
"nichž se domníval, že ohrožují mladé stromky."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"Ougl was quick to guess that the death of any Elder Wose would only further "
"enrage the treefolk, and resolved to keep his distance from them."
msgstr ""
"Ougl si rychle uvědomil, že smrt kteréhokoli z prastarých stromovců by lesní "
"lid jen více rozzuřila a rozhodl se od nich držet dál."

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1156
msgid "Death of any of the Elder Woses located on the Great Trees"
msgstr "Kterýkoli ze strážců háje stojících u velkých stromů zemře"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1188
msgid ""
"With the death of one of the three great guardians of the grove, the woses "
"went into a frenzy. The trolls, helpless in the face of these strange new "
"creatures, knew it was their end."
msgstr ""
"Po smrti jednoho ze tří velkých strážců háje propadli stromovci zuřivosti. "
"Trollové, kteří byli vůči těmto podivným novým tvorům bezmocní, věděli, že "
"je to jejich konec."

#. [message]: speaker=OM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1242
msgid "O m m m...!!"
msgstr "O m m m...!!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1248
msgid ""
"As the sound of battle echoed through the grove, a great old tree finally "
"began to stir."
msgstr ""
"Zatímco se hájem rozléhal lomoz bitvy, jeden mohutný a velmi starý strom se "
"najednou začal hýbat."

#. [message]: speaker=OM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1263
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1273
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1353
msgid "O m m m..."
msgstr "O m m m..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1316
msgid ""
"The awakened Wose Shaman spoke to Ougl in a strange way, and Ougl "
"understood. The Wose’s name was Ommm, and it was the leader of the tree folk."
msgstr ""
"Probuzený stromový šaman promluvil k Ouglovi podivným způsobem a Ougl mu "
"porozuměl. Jmenoval se Ommm a byl vůdcem stromového lidu."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1327
msgid ""
"Ommm used a mysterious magic to see the purpose of the troll’s journey, and "
"whether they had evil intentions towards the green grove."
msgstr ""
"Ommm použil tajemnou magii, aby zjistil, jaký je účel trollovy cesty a zda "
"má zlé úmysly vůči zelenému háji."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1333
msgid ""
"It soon realized that the trolls were not to blame for the unfortunate "
"skirmish."
msgstr "Brzy si uvědomil, že potyčku vyvolalo nedorozumění."

#. [message]: speaker=OM
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1338
msgid "O m m m...?"
msgstr "O m m m...?"

#. [message]: speaker=OL
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1348
msgid "Ougl..."
msgstr "Ougl..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1359
msgid ""
"Ougl wanted to travel further upwards, but the Wose Shaman advised him "
"against it. The woses warned that the surface held many creatures who were "
"not guided by goodness of heart, but by the law of strength."
msgstr ""
"Ougl chtěl putovat ještě výš, ale stromový šaman mu to rozmlouval. Varoval "
"ho, že na povrchu žije mnoho tvorů, kteří se neřídí dobrotou srdce, ale "
"právem silnějšího."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1365
msgid ""
"But Ougl had seen green lands now, and he began to dream of seeing more. The "
"higher he climbed, the more green there would be."
msgstr ""
"Ougla však zcela okouzlila zelenavá krajina a toužil po tom, uvidět jí ještě "
"více. A cesta za další zelení vedla nahoru."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1382
msgid ""
"After some thought, the Wose Shaman agreed to give the trolls directions to "
"the surface. But the trolls were to first plant new trees in place of the "
"ones that had fallen during the battle."
msgstr ""
"Stromový šaman dlouze přemýšlel nad osudem a pomocí kamenných bytostí. "
"Nakonec souhlasil, že trollům pomůže a ukáže jim cestu na povrch. Nejprve "
"však bylo nutné zasadit nové stromky, aby nahradily ty, jež padly v bitvě."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/02_A_Dream.cfg:1391
msgid ""
"After some thought, the Wose Shaman agreed to give the trolls directions to "
"the surface, but again warned Ougl that sometimes dreams are better left in "
"the realm of dreams."
msgstr ""
"Stromový šaman dlouze přemýšlel nad osudem a pomocí kamenných bytostí. "
"Nakonec souhlasil, že trollům pomůže a ukáže jim cestu na povrch, avšak "
"varoval Ougla, že občas je moudřejší, aby sny zůstaly pouze sny."

#. [scenario]: id=03_Fateful_Day
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:5
msgid "Fateful Day"
msgstr "Osudný den"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The Wose Shaman, as promised, told the trolls where they should go to get "
"out of the caves."
msgstr ""
"Stromový šaman, dle slibu, řekl trollům, kudy se mají vydat, aby se dostali "
"z jeskyní."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:31
msgid ""
"It also put a peculiar charm on Ougl, allowing him to understand the speech "
"of other beings despite not knowing how to speak himself."
msgstr ""
"Ougl byl díky tomuto podivuhodnému setkání obdařen schopností porozumět řeči "
"ostatních bytostí, přestože sám mluvit neuměl."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:35
msgid ""
"The trolls soon left the woses and continued on their journey. The going was "
"difficult, for the rocks they now climbed were very earthy and crumbly."
msgstr ""
"Trollové brzy opustili stromový lid a pokračovali dál sami. Cesta byla "
"náročná, protože skály, po kterých nyní šplhali, byly velmi prašné a drolivé."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:39
msgid ""
"There was also less food than on the deeper levels. The trolls found only "
"mushrooms, and Ougl disliked mushrooms. But this did not discourage him, for "
"Ougl now had a dream and a goal for his trek."
msgstr ""
"Jídla zde bylo také méně než v hlubinách. Trollové nacházeli jen houby a "
"Ougl houby neměl rád. To ho však neodradilo, neboť měl svůj sen a nyní i cíl "
"své cesty."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:43
msgid "Despite their incautious nature, trolls are not simple at all."
msgstr "Navzdory své neohrabanosti nejsou trollové vůbec hloupí."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:47
msgid ""
"When they tame their inner flame, they move in the realm of feelings and can "
"guess the intentions of others without the need for speech."
msgstr ""
"Pokud dokáží zkrotit svůj vnitřní plamen, mohou se pohybovat v říši pocitů a "
"odhadnout úmysly druhých, bez znalosti řeči."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:51
msgid ""
"Ougl and his friends knew from the beginning that the tree folk were not "
"evil, and they did not understand why the trees decided to attack them. If "
"the trolls had done nothing wrong, then why were they attacked?"
msgstr ""
"Ougl a jeho přátelé od začátku věděli, že stromoví lidé nejsou zlí, a "
"nechápali, proč se stromy rozhodly na ně zaútočit. Co je k tomu vedlo?"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:56
msgid ""
"The Golden Flame Tribe thought for a long time about what had happened and "
"what might yet happen. After much travel and much thought, they happened "
"across an underground lake."
msgstr ""
"Kmen Zlatého plamene dlouho přemýšlel o tom, co se stalo a co by se ještě "
"mohlo stát. Po dlouhém putování a mnoha úvahách narazili na podzemní jezero."

#. [side]: type=Naga Warrior, id=SA, gender=female
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:89
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/04_A_Beautiful_World.cfg:58
msgid "Purple Eye Naga"
msgstr "Naga purpurového oka"

#. [side]: type=Naga Warrior, id=SA, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:94
msgid "Sessa Purple Eye"
msgstr "Sessa purpurové oko"

#. [side]: type=Naga Warrior, id=SA, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:125
msgid "Irxa"
msgstr "Irxa"

#. [side]: type=Naga Warrior, id=SA, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:126
msgid "Neillei"
msgstr "Neillei"

#. [side]: type=Naga Warrior, id=SA, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Dusk_of_Dawn/scenarios/03_Fateful_Day.cfg:127
msgid "Oaserss"
msgstr "Oaserss"

